    <section id="H681463377A0B4B3BBDDCFE22C751D2B0">
      <enum>4.</enum>
      <header>Effective
			 date</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">The amendments made by
			 this Act shall apply with respect to monthly insurance benefits payable under
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" value="Social Security Act/t:II" entity-type="act">title II of the Social Security Act</cato:entity-ref> for months after December 2013.
			 Notwithstanding <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" value="Social Security Act/s:215/ss:f" entity-type="act">section 215(f) of the Social Security Act</cato:entity-ref>, the <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-id="2800" entity-type="federal-body">Commissioner of
			 Social Security</cato:entity-ref> shall adjust primary insurance amounts to the extent necessary
			 to take into account the amendments made by <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" proposed="true" value="Social Security Fairness Act of 2013/s:3" entity-type="act">section 3</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
